pos_examples: Now, saw board bastion into large part kumquat using saw screen with awood socket, surface fire, changing size from aboardsize frame_9 to aboardsize frame_9_75 through aboardsize frame_9_21 and aboardsize frame_9_75_83.
(do-saw-large bastion kumquat screen socket fire frame_9 frame_9_75_83 frame_9_21 frame_9_75)

Once you are done, please saw board bastion into medium part kumquat using saw screen with awood socket, surface fire, changing size from aboardsize frame_9_21 to aboardsize frame_9 through aboardsize frame_9_75.
(do-saw-medium bastion kumquat screen socket fire frame_9_21 frame_9_75 frame_9)

First, do immersion varnish on part kumquat using immersion-varnisher roof_11 to change color to acolour dress_red with surface fire and then saw board bastion into small part kumquat using saw screen with awood socket, surface fire, changing size from aboardsize frame_9 to aboardsize frame_9_21.

(do-immersion-varnish kumquat roof_11 dress_red fire)
(do-saw-small bastion kumquat screen socket fire frame_9 frame_9_21)

The next step is to do grind on part kumquat using grinder teddy to change surface from surface fire to verysmooth, color from acolour object_50 to natural, and treatment from treatmentstatus kumquat_8 to treatmentstatus kumquat_8_98.
(do-grind kumquat teddy fire object_50 kumquat_8 kumquat_8_98)
